description:
Are you in need of faith? Is faith something that dwells inward or appears outward?  Can we still honor God while disobeying His guidance? God assures us not to fear, for He promises to care for His people. Move forward confidently in faith, knowing that God provides and works all things for our good. Explore how obedience and standing firm for God is of critical importance now, as we are living in the Day of Atonement. Go forward in victory.
